McAfee MEP => Includes a range of security features such as antivirus, anti-malware, firewall, intrusion detection and prevention, and web security.
Microsoft LDE => Microsoft offers a disk encryption technology called BitLocker that provides full disk encryption for laptops and desktops running Windows operating system.
